{"tid":735700,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"西客係咪真係有樣睇","createTime":"2018-07-09T16:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T17:57:43.000Z","uid":17189,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecce090631c1e68605cb325a700f56751fe5bbd5","tid":735700,"uid":17189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T16:25:51.000Z","msg":"以前做過好多服務業既工作<br />\n唔知有冇人同我一樣有啲人個樣一睇就知係西客好撚柒麻煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以做番白領既我都唔會為難服務業既同事<br />\n因為都感受過做服務業既慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成撚日比啲麻煩西客為難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尤其最多就係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係呀話緊你地班死港豬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以為比小小錢就大撚曬咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b28d91466179eac13b2c53068f6927b6fa0d3b","tid":735700,"uid":111375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T17:57:43.000Z","msg":"以前大學part time 做過連鎖壽司鋪樓面<br />\n有啲讀過幾粒英文字嘅閪客見你做侍應就會扮高尚睇你唔起<br />\n所以而家畢業完做返白領都會唔該前唔該後<br />\n其實你對人好 人地咪自然對返你好 <br />\n茶都幫你refill快啲啦 <br />\n大家都係講互相尊重姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}